@startuml PlatformRoadmap
' Combined roadmap: Center Control (C1–C6) and Tenant (T1–T6)

skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam handwritten false
skinparam defaultTextAlignment center

title Platform Roadmap – Center Control (C1–C6) & Tenant (T1–T6)

' Use two parallel lifelines to illustrate evolution

' Center Control timeline
concise "Center Control (Control Plane)" as CC {
  @0
  CC is C1 : Platform Foundations – Multi-Tenant Ready
  @1
  CC is C2 : Tenant Lifecycle & Basic Governance
  @2
  CC is C3 : Plan/Package, Feature Toggles & Billing Readiness
  @3
  CC is C4 : Cross-Tenant Monitoring, Audit & Compliance
  @4
  CC is C5 : Ecosystem Integrations & Marketplace Management
  @5
  CC is C6 : Data, Analytics & AI-Driven Operations
}

' Tenant timeline (per-tenant view, conceptual)
concise "Tenant E-Commerce (Per Tenant)" as TEN {
  @0
  TEN is T1 : Tenant Not Onboarded
  @1
  TEN is T2 : Tenant Onboarded – Store Not Live
  @2
  TEN is T3 : Tenant Live – Core E-Commerce (MVP)
  @3
  TEN is T4 : Tenant Live – Advanced Catalog & Multi-Store
  @4
  TEN is T5 : Tenant Live – Integrations & POS
  @5
  TEN is T6 : Tenant Live – Loyalty/Royalty & AI-Driven
}

' Visual hints for dependencies (comments only for human readers)
' - Before T2, need at least C1–C2
' - Before T3, need at least C2–C3
' - Before T4, need at least C3–C4
' - Before T5, need at least C3–C5
' - Before T6, need at least C3–C6

@enduml
